% TIMESTEPPING%% Files%   box_heat                 - solve heat equation in box-shaped domain%   cavityflowmovie          - cavity flow solution animation%   channelflowmovie         - channel flow solution animation%   colamdAxB                - refined saddlepoint system solver%   defaultAxB               - standard MATLAB saddlepoint system solver%   dtflowbc                 - imposes updated BC at the current timestep%   dtheatbc                 - imposes Dirichlet BC at the current timestep%   ell_heat                 - solve heat equation in L-shaped domain%   energymeanvorticity      - compute acceleration and mean vorticity%   helpme_heat              - heat equation interactive help %   helpme_timestepping      - unsteady problem solution interactive help %   helpme_unsteady_cd       - unsteady CD problem interactive help %   helpme_unsteady_navier   - unsteady flow problem interactive help %   obstacleflowmovie        - obstacle flow solution animation%   resetflowbc              - resets boundary values in unsteady flow%   resetheatbc              - resets boundary values in unsteady diffusion%   restart_navier           - restart unsteady flow in cavity domain%   restart_channel_navier   - restart unsteady flow in channel domain%   restart_obstacle_navier  - restart unsteady flow in obstacle domain%   restart_step_navier      - restart unsteady flow in step domain%   setmovietype             - assign movie format%   stabtr                   - standard integrator based on stabilized TR%   stabtrNS                 - Navier-Stokes integrator using stabilized TR%   stabtrX                  - vanilla stabilised TR | extended%   stepflowmovie            - step flow solution animation%   step_heat                - solve heat equation in backward step domain%   unsteady_cd              - unsteady CD problem in square domain %   unsteady_navier          - unsteady flow problem in square domain%   unsteady_channel_navier  - solve Navier-Stokes problem in channel domain%   unsteady_obstacle_navier - unsteady flow problem in obstacle domain%   unsteady_step_navier     - solve Navier-Stokes problem in step domain%   unsteadyflowbc           - imposes inflow boundary condition %   xxheatbc                 - hot wall Dirichlet boundary condition%   xxstreambc               - dynamic Dirichlet BC on streamfunction